Subject: Service Bulletin FB-2025-09 - Revised Lubrication Interval - FD Fan Model AXF-900
Date: Tue, 09 Dec 2025 14:05:00 +0530
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset="utf-8"

Dear Customer,

This bulletin applies to AXF-900 series forced draft fans (your unit: FD-2).

Field data from high-ash coal and biomass sites shows accelerated grease
degradation. Effective immediately, the recommended bearing lubrication
interval is revised:

  OLD: every 500 running hours
  NEW: every 250 running hours (high-ash environments)

Failure to adopt the revised interval may lead to lubrication starvation,
elevated bearing temperature and trip. Please update your SOPs and confirm
adoption within 30 days.

Action owner at your site (per our records): N. Iyer, Maintenance Planning.

Regards,
